{[%evp 0,83,38,22,22,22,22,22,27,3,3,3,6,14,6,6,15,-16,-6,-8,8,-2,5,3,14,17,21,17,28,34,38,33,45,31,43,31,64,47,41,19,53,45,82,71,93,55,100,36,38,13,41,4,87,98,102,85,166,76,110,114,98,67,86,99,104,83,82,60,101,102,83,1,19,-28,28,-183,27,27,222,253,317,192,757,792,544,918] do not allow Nf5 !} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 Nf6 5. O-O Be7 6. Re1 b5 7. Bb3 d6 8. c3 O-O 9. h3 Nb8 10. d4 Nbd7 11. Nbd2 Bb7 12. Bc2 Re8 13. Nf1 Bf8 14. Ng3 c5 15. d5 c4 (15... g6 $1) 16. Bg5 (16. b4 $5 cxb3 17. axb3 Qc7 18. Bd2 Rac8 (18... a5 19. Bd3) 19. Bd3 Nc5 20. Bf1 g6 21. c4 $16) ({Anand didn't hurry with this because of the Nc5, followed by Bc8-f5} 16. Nf5 Nc5 {[%cal Rb7c8]}) 16... Qc7 (16... g6 $1 17. Qd2) 17. Nf5 $14 {Finally, the knight comes to f5} Kh8 18. g4 Ng8 19. Qd2 Nc5 20. Be3 Bc8 21. Ng3 Rb8 22. Kg2 a5 23. a3 Ne7 24. Rh1 Ng6 25. g5 b4 26. axb4 axb4 27. cxb4 Na6 28. Ra4 Nf4+ 29. Bxf4 exf4 30. Nh5 Qb6 31. Qxf4 Nxb4 32. Bb1 Rb7 33. Ra3 Rc7 34. Rd1 Na6 35. Nd4 Qxb2 36. Rg3 c3 37. Nf6 Re5 38. g6 fxg6 39. Nd7 Be7 40. Nxe5 dxe5 41. Qf7 h6 42. Qe8+ 1-0

