{in this game ..white might be slightly better objectively, but black is very solid and he has counterplay} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 d6 5. Bxc6+ bxc6 6. d4 f6 7. c4 g6 8. Nc3 Bg7 9. Be3 Ne7 10. Qc2 O-O 11. O-O-O $2 (11. O-O exd4 12. Nxd4 (12. Bxd4 $2 c5 13. Be3 f5 (13... Bb7)) 12... c5 13. Nde2 f5 (13... Bb7)) 11... Be6 $15 (11... Qe8 $3 $15) 12. c5 d5 13. h4 Qe8 14. h5 gxh5 15. dxe5 fxe5 16. Ng5 Bd7 17. Qe2 h6 18. Rxh5 hxg5 19. exd5 cxd5 20. Bxg5 c6 21. Rdh1 e4 22. Bh6 Nf5 23. Bxg7 Nxg7 24. Rh8+ Kf7 25. R8h6 Qe5 26. Qd2 Be6 27. Ne2 d4 28. Rh7 e3 29. Qxd4 Qxd4 30. Nxd4 exf2 31. Rxg7+ Kxg7 32. Nxe6+ Kg6 33. Nxf8+ Rxf8 34. Rf1 Kg5 35. Kd2 Kg4 36. Ke2 Kg3 0-1

