{[%evp 0,86,22,33,31,31,31,31,33,-4,14,14,33,9,45,45,45,18,12,-10,-2,-10,30,-10,-18,-58,-75,-99,-116,-161,-160,-160,-160,-99,-124,-75,-121,-193,-193,-163,-112,-155,-161,-124,-136,-146,-107,-157,-157,-148,-148,-175,-159,-253,-162,-254,-245,-242,-242,-252,-216,-248,-176,-258,-151,-267,-208,-282,-199,-226,-223,-250,-215,-234,-207,-247,-263,-262,-263,-299,-246,-422,-239,-422,-336,-585,-594,-1029,-1079] A very easy win by Black because White allowed this 9. ..b5! move and later got very optimistic with this Ng5-Ne6 which is nothing really good!} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 d6 5. O-O Bd7 6. c3 g6 7. d4 Bg7 8. d5 Nce7 9. c4 b5 10. Bc2 f5 11. Ng5 Nf6 12. a4 bxc4 13. f3 c6 14. dxc6 Qb6+ 15. Kh1 Qxc6 16. a5 O-O 17. Ba4 Qc7 18. Bxd7 Qxd7 19. Qa4 Rfc8 20. Rd1 Rc6 21. Nc3 h6 22. Nh3 Qe6 23. Nf2 d5 24. exd5 Nexd5 25. Bd2 Rb8 26. Qa2 Nb4 27. Qa4 Nd3 28. Nxd3 cxd3 29. Rab1 Nd5 30. Re1 Nxc3 31. Bxc3 Qd5 32. Rbd1 Re6 33. Rf1 Rbe8 34. Qa3 h5 35. h3 e4 36. Bxg7 Kxg7 37. fxe4 fxe4 38. Qc3+ Qe5 39. Qc4 R8e7 40. Qc8 Rf6 41. Rfe1 Qd4 42. Rf1 e3 43. Rxf6 Qxf6 0-1

