{[%evp 0,98,28,28,11,29,29,16,16,-16,-3,3,12,12,26,20,32,0,-11,-27,-16,-13,-10,-8,0,-1,37,19,28,-16,-29,-77,-48,-88,-41,-63,-11,-26,-24,-22,-22,-22,-17,-2,-9,-47,-50,-58,-63,-50,-55,-96,-96,-84,-115,-115,-115,-80,-93,-88,-84,-73,-69,-189,-218,-167,-113,-110,-91,-91,-87,-77,-75,-72,-70,-65,-65,-77,-29,-16,-21,-10,-22,-22,-25,-9,0,-40,-31,-4,-39,-74,-47,-195,-283,-544,-551,-573,-616,-590,-608]} 1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bb5 a6 4. Ba4 Nf6 5. d3 b5 {Not accurate! Be careful when you play to avoid mixing up the moves. on 5. d3 we play d6.} (5... d6 $1 6. c3 g6 {[%cal Yf8g7]}) 6. Bb3 Be7 (6... g6 7. Ng5 {Not enough time for this idea now.} d5 8. exd5 Nxd5 9. Qf3 Be6 $18) 7. O-O d6 8. c3 O-O 9. Re1 Na5 10. Bc2 c5 11. Nbd2 Re8 12. Nf1 Bf8 $2 {Black makes a mistake. 12...h6 was correct!} (12... h6 $1 13. Ng3 Nc6 $132 (13... Bf8 $132)) 13. h3 $6 (13. Bg5 $1 h6 14. Bxf6 Qxf6 15. Ne3 $14) 13... Bb7 14. N3h2 $6 (14. Bg5 $1 Nc6 15. Ne3 h6 16. Bxf6 Qxf6 17. Bb3 $16) 14... d5 15. Qe2 c4 (15... d4 $15 {Very good move as well.} 16. cxd4 exd4 $15) 16. dxc4 Nxc4 17. Ng3 Nxe4 18. Nxe4 dxe4 19. Bxe4 Bxe4 20. Qxe4 Qd7 {White lost too much time, and Black is already better, which led to winning the game.} 21. Nf3 f5 22. Qe2 e4 23. Nd4 Ne5 24. Rd1 Nd3 25. Nc2 f4 26. Ne1 f3 27. Qf1 fxg2 28. Qxg2 Rad8 29. Bg5 Be7 30. Nxd3 exd3 31. Bxe7 Rxe7 32. Rd2 Re2 33. Rad1 Rxd2 34. Rxd2 Qe6 35. Qg5 Rd5 36. Qe3 Qg6+ 37. Kh2 h6 38. b3 Rg5 39. f4 Rd5 40. c4 bxc4 41. bxc4 Rd8 42. c5 h5 43. Qf3 Qf5 44. c6 Qc5 45. f5 Qc3 46. Rg2 Qe5+ 47. Qg3 Qxg3+ 48. Kxg3 d2 49. c7 d1=Q 0-1

